**/target/

# Generated WASM build artifacts
*.wat
*.wasm

# OS / editor
.DS_Store

# Local-only context scratchpad (chat transcripts the maintainer keeps to refresh
# an agent's context across sessions). Intentionally untracked.
PAST.md
